  "page": "Gareth Tyrell",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/50px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/75px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/100px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> High Steward</span><br />Gareth Tyrell</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\"><img alt=\"House Tyrell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/50px-House_Tyrell.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/75px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/House_Tyrell.svg/100px-House_Tyrell.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/High_Steward\" title=\"High Steward\">High Steward</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Tyrell\" title=\"Alester Tyrell\">Alester Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Gareth)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Gareth)\">Leo Tyrell</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gareth Tyrell</b> was a head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a> and the first <a href=\"/index.php/High_Steward\" title=\"High Steward\">High Steward</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a> for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">House Gardener</a>. He was the second son of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Tyrell\" title=\"Alester Tyrell\">Alester Tyrell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gareth_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Unlike his elder brother, Gareth was of a more bookish bent and never achieved <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighthood</a>, choosing to serve as a royal steward instead.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gareth_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Gareth and his son <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Tyrell_(son_of_Gareth)\" title=\"Leo Tyrell (son of Gareth)\">Leo</a> performed their duties so well that the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Gardener\" title=\"House Gardener\">Gardeners</a> made the office of High Steward hereditary.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reach:_house_tyrell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gareth_Tyrell&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\">